snippet: Second-ranked Henrik Stenson shot an 8-under 64 to share the third-round lead with England’s Eddie Pepperell at the Nordea Masters on Saturday.
lead_paragraph: Second-ranked Henrik Stenson shot an 8-under 64 to share the third-round lead with England’s Eddie Pepperell at the Nordea Masters on Saturday.

headline.main: Henrik Stenson Shares Lead in Sweden
headline.print_headline: Stenson surges to lead at Nordea Masters
